">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Thu%E1%BB%B5-Chi/M%E1%BA%ADu-Th%C3%ACn-xu%C3%A2n-du-Long-%C4%90%E1%BB%99i-s%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-vFyLNHjIdIKOd6KEZSeY-w">Mậu Thìn xuân du Long Đội sơn tự - 戊辰春遊龍隊山寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Thu%E1%BB%B5-Chi/author-Ya8ICdCs1Ab5sFLe9rk-Pw">Hoàng Thuỵ Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Thu%E1%BB%B7-li%E1%BB%85u/poem-n2jCNzT17fugYXAO61bmbw">Thuỷ liễu - 水柳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Tu%C3%BD-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Phi-c%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-RygIdhfXH676fgW916uOpQ">Tuý Dương Phi cúc kỳ 1 - 醉楊妃菊其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/T%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem--xqZEuf6P9hQXDGcDKUZ5A">Tức cảnh kỳ 2 - 即景其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-%C4%90%C3%B4n-Nho/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ki%E1%BA%BFn-hoan-Kim-L%C4%83ng-th%C3%A0nh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-t%C3%A2y-l%C3%A2u/poem-W6FzoN5oc4zKWgkqIYs-5A">Tương kiến hoan (Kim Lăng thành thượng tây lâu) - 相見歡（金陵城上西樓）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-%C4%90%C3%B4n-Nho/author-tMxVgH-MSjJbaW_gVlSSZw">Chu Đôn Nho</a>)<br></div>	</div>
